reviews.text: easy to access. fast food with fair price. not crowd even during peak hours. English menu provided.

This is a large branch of Yoshinoya. You can get beef bowls and other types of rice bowls here. The food is delicious and consistent. You can pay with a credit card or an octopus card here. Of course cash is accepted. This is pretty much a self service branch so feel free to get your cutlery and condiments yourself when your food is ready, they'll call your name.
Getting more expensive and the food is not as good as before.
The usual fast food beef rice chain store
Fair hot pot , crowd and staff is not enough to support the whole, lack of refill of soups
